    <br><br>
    <font face="Arial" size="2">
    <b>Date of Birth Search Support!</b><br><br>
    You can search for a person using three different methods of date of birth -- Month/Year (mm/yyyy), Month/Date/Year (mm/dd/yyyy), or Year (yyyy).
    <br><br>
    <b>Date of Birth and First Name!</b><br><br>
    You can search for a person using their full date of birth and first name.&nbsp;&nbsp;The search can be narrowed by adding a state, city and state, or Zip Code.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can even add a radius when searching with city and state or Zip Code.
    <br><br>
    <b>Nickname Support!</b><br><br>
    If you specify a first name nickname when performing a Person Search, we automatically perform the search and return results matching the person's proper name.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you wish to turn off this intuitive feature, simply uncheck the Use Nickname box on the search screen.
